Package org.whiteflagprotocol.java.crypto

Whiteflag Protocol Crypto Library

This package provides a library that defines Whiteflag cryptographic features as specified in the Whiteflag standard in Java. It contains all implementation independent cryptogrpahic functionality used by the main protocol classes. Seperating these critical security functions makes them better inspectable, testable and maintainable.
